            Homeowners Property Tax Exemption. Provide a copy of the current property tax bill indicating this exemption has
            been applied for by the qualified owner occupant(s)
        </li>
        <li>
            Form 11: Affidavit for Ownership / Occupancy (must be signed and notarized)
        </li>
    </ul>
</p>
<p>
