<h4 id="myEcpGuidelinesTenantIntent">Tentant Intent - Purchase & Tenant Intent - ECP Lifetime Lease</h4>
<p>
    Tenant Intent to Purchase and/or Tenant Into to Accept Offer of Lifetime Lease [Sec. 1388]
</p>
<p>
    Submit these forms properly signed to represent the required number of occupants (owners or tenants)
    who have indicated their intent to either purchase their unit or accept the ECP lifetime lease when it is offered.
</p>
<p>
    For a 2-unit building, applicant must submit at least one (1) signed Tenant Intent Forms. For a 3 - 5 unit building,
    at least two (2) signed Forms are required, and for a 6 unit building, at least three (3) signed Forms are required.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Note:</strong> All tenant(s) must be offered the ECP lifetime lease (regardless of whether they have signed
