</p>

<h4 id="myEcpGuidelinesAckFees">Acknowledgment of Fees</h4>
<p>
    Submit Acknowledgement of Fees Form properly signed. [Sec. 1323 (6)]. Electronic signatures or scanned copies of wet signatures of
