</p>

<h4 id="myEcpGuidelinesReleaseOfCommonAreas">Owner's Affidavit - Release in Common Areas</h4>
<p>
    The Owner's Release in Interest Form properly signed. Electronic signatures or scanned copies of wet signatures of
