<p>
    Submit completed Subdivider's Statement A Form, which includes a statement indicating that the notice of proposed conversion has been
    given to any lessees or tenants subsequent to the submission of the application packet for conversion. Electronic signatures or
    scanned copies of wet signatures of all owners in pdf format are acceptable.
</p>

<h4 id="myEcpGuidelinesNewTenantNotice">Subdivider's Notice to New Tenants</h4>
<p>
    Subdivider’s commitment to provide notice of conversion to new tenants [Sec. 1381(a)(6)(C)]
</p>
<p>
    Submit completed Subdivider's Statement B Form, which includes a statement indicating that the notice of proposed conversion will be given to any lessees
    or tenants subsequent to the submission of the application packet for conversion. Electronic signatures or scanned copies of wet
    signatures of all owners in pdf format are acceptable.
</p>

<h4 id="myEcpGuidelinesRightOfRefusal">Tenant Right of Refusal</h4>
<p>
    Subdivider’s commitment to provide a right of first refusal to tenants to purchase their units [Sec. 1387]
    Submit completed Tenant Right of First Refusal Form.   Electronic signatures or scanned copies of wet signatures of all owners
    in pdf format are acceptable.
</p>

